title: Apple iPhone 14 Pro
description:
Apple iPhone 14 Pro comes with a 6.1 inches LTPO Super Retina XDR OLED 1179 x 2556 pixels screen. It has a double punch-hole design. The back camera is of quad 48+12+12 Megapixel + TOF 3D LiDAR scanner with powerful image processing capability and 4K video recording. The front one is of Dual 12 MP and SL 3D camera. Apple iPhone 14 Pro comes with – mAh battery with – fast charging solution. It has 6 GB RAM, up to 3.46 GHz Hexa-core CPU and Apple GPU. It is powered by a 4 nm Apple A16 Bionic chipset. The device comes with 128, 256, 512 GB or 1 TB internal storage.

Among other features, there is Face ID, Apple Pay, Siri, Qi Wireless Charging, Emergency SOS via satellite etc. There is no FM Radio, 3.5mm jack and MicroSD slot in this phone. The device is IP68 certified waterproof and 5G supported.

title: Apple iPhone 14
description:
Apple iPhone 14 comes with a 6.1 inches Super Retina XDR OLED Full HD+ screen. It has a classical Apple iPhone notch design. The back camera is of dual 12+12 MP with powerful image processing capability and 4K video recording. The front one is of Dual 12 MP and SL 3D camera. Apple iPhone 14 comes with – mAh battery with – fast charging solution. It has 4 GB RAM, up to 3.23 GHz Hexa-core CPU and Apple GPU. It is powered by a 5 nm Apple A15 Bionic chipset. The device comes with 128, 256 or 512 GB internal storage.

Among other features, there is Face ID, Apple Pay, Siri, Qi Wireless Charging, Emergency SOS via satellite etc. There is no FM Radio, 3.5mm jack and MicroSD slot in this phone. The device is IP68 certified waterproof and 5G supported.

title: Apple iPhone 13 Pro Max
description: Apple iPhone 13 Pro Max comes with a 6.7 inches Super Retina XDR OLED Full HD+ screen. It has a Apple iPhone notch design. The back camera is of quad 12+12+12 Megapixel + TOF 3D LiDAR scanner with powerful image processing capability and 4K video recording. The front one is of Dual 12 MP and SL 3D camera. Apple iPhone 13 Pro Max comes with 4352 mAh battery with 27W fast charging solution. It has 6 GB RAM, up to 3.22 GHz Hexa-core CPU and Apple GPU. It is powered by a 5 nm Apple A15 Bionic chipset. The device comes with 128, 256, 512 GB or 1 TB internal storage.

title: Apple iPhone 12 Pro Max
description: Apple iPhone 12 Pro Max comes with a 6.7 inches Super Retina XDR OLED screen which is one of its main specialties. It has a classical Apple iPhone notch design. The back camera is of quad 12+12+12 MP + TOF 3D with powerful image processing capability and Ultra HD 4K video recording. The front one is of Dual 12 MP and SL 3D camera. Apple iPhone 12 Pro Max comes with Li-ion battery with 18W fast charging solution. It has 6 GB RAM, Hexa-core CPU and Apple GPU. It is powered by a 5 nm Apple A14 Bionic chipset. The device comes with 128, 256 or 512 GB internal storage.

title: Xiaomi 12 Pro
description: Xiaomi 12 Pro comes with 6.73 inches Quad HD+ LTPO AMOLED screen. It has a Full-View center punch-hole design. The frontside is protected by a Gorilla Glass Victus. The back camera is of triple 50+50+50 MP with dual-Pixel PDAF, dual-LED flash, 115º ultrawide lens, telephoto camera, OIS, 2x optical zoom, 1/1.28″, 1.22µm, etc. and up to 8K video recording. The front camera is of 32 MP. Xiaomi 12 Pro comes with 4600 mAh battery with 120W Quick Charge 4+ fast charging and 50W Fast Wireless Charging options. It has 8 or 12 GB RAM, up to 3 GHz octa-core CPU and Adreno 730 GPU. It is powered by a Qualcomm Snapdragon 8 Gen 1 (4 nm) chipset. The device comes in 128 or 256 GB UFS 3.1 internal storage and no Memory Card slot. There is an optical in-display fingerprint sensor in this phone.

title: Xiaomi 11T
description: Xiaomi 11T comes with 6.67 inches Full HD+ AMOLED screen. It has a Full-View center punch-hole design. The frontside is protected by a Gorilla Glass Victus. The back camera is of triple 108+8+5 MP with PDAF, dual-LED flash, ultrawide, telephoto macro camera, etc. and 4K video recording. The front camera is of 16 MP. 11T comes with 5000 mAh battery with 67W fast charging. It has 8 GB RAM, up to 3.0 GHz octa-core CPU and Mali-G77 MC9 GPU. It is powered by a MediaTek Dimensity 1200 5G (6 nm) chipset. The device comes in 128 or 256 GB UFS 3.1 internal storage and no Memory Card slot. There is a side-mounted fingerprint sensor in this phone.

title: Xiaomi Mi 11X 5G
description: Xiaomi Mi 11X 5G comes with 6.67 inches Full HD+ Super AMOLED screen. It has a Full-View punch-hole design. Both front and backside are protected by 5th generation Gorilla Glasses. The back camera is of triple 48+8+5 MP with PDAF, LED flash, ultrawide, dedicated macro camera, etc. and 4K video recording. The front camera is of 20 MP. Mi 11X comes with 4520 mAh battery with 33W fast charging. It has 6 or 8 GB RAM, up to 3.2 GHz octa-core CPU and Adreno 650 GPU. It is powered by a Qualcomm Snapdragon 870 5G (7 nm) chipset. The device comes in 128 GB UFS 3.1 internal storage and no external Memory Card slot. There is aside-mounted fingerprint sensor in this phone.

title: Samsung Galaxy S22+
description: Samsung Galaxy S22+ comes with 6.6 inches Full HD+ Dynamic AMOLED 2X screen. It has a punch-hole front camera design. The back camera is of triple 50+10+12 MP with Dual Pixel PDAF, telephoto, OIS, ultrawide, 3x optical zoom etc. and 8K video recording. The front camera is of 10 Megapixel. Galaxy S22+ comes with 4500 mAh battery with 45W fast charging. It has 12 GB RAM, up to 3.0 GHz octa-core CPU and Adreno 730 GPU. It is powered by a Qualcomm Snapdragon 8 Gen 1 (4 nm) chipset. The device comes with 256 GB UFS 3.1 internal storage and no MicroSD slot. There is an ultrasonic in-display fingerprint sensor in this phone.

title: Samsung Galaxy A52s 5G
description: Samsung Galaxy A52s 5G comes with 6.5 inches Full HD+ Super AMOLED screen. It has a center punch-hole front camera design. The back camera is of Quad 64+12+5+5 with PDAF, OIS, ultrawide, depth sensor, dedicated macro camera etc. and Ultra HD video recording. The front camera is of 32 MP. Galaxy A52s 5G comes with 4500 mAh battery with 25W fast charging. It has 8 GB RAM, up to 2.3 GHz octa-core CPU and Adreno 618 GPU. It is powered by a Qualcomm Snapdragon 720G (8 nm) chipset. The device comes with 128 GB internal storage and shared MicroSD slot. There is an in-display optical fingerprint sensor in this phone.

title: OnePlus 10 Pro 5G
description: OnePlus 10 Pro 5G comes with 6.7 inches QHD+ LTPO2 Fluid AMOLED screen. It has a left punch-hole front camera design. The back camera is of triple 48+8+50 MP with multi-directional PDAF, Laser autofocus, optical image stabilization, f/1.7 aperture, dual-LED flash, 150º ultrawide, telephoto, 3.3x optical zoom, Hasselblad Color Calibration etc. and 8K video recording. The front camera is of 32 Megapixel. OnePlus 10 Pro 5G comes with 5000 mAh battery with 80W fast charging and 50W fast wireless charging. It has 8 or 12 GB RAM, up to 3.0 GHz octa-core CPU and Adreno 730 GPU. It is powered by a Qualcomm Snapdragon 8 Gen 1 (4 nm) chipset. The device comes with 256 GB internal storage and no MicroSD slot. There is an optical in-display fingerprint sensor in this phone.

title: OnePlus 8 Pro
description: OnePlus 8 Pro comes with 6.78 inches QHD+ Fluid AMOLED screen. It has a punch-hole front camera design. The back camera is of quad 48+8+48+5 MP with omnidirectional PDAF, Laser autofocus, OIS, ultrawide, telephoto, 3x optical zoom, depth sensor, dual-LED flash etc. and Ultra HD video recording. The front camera is of 16 Megapixel. OnePlus 8 Pro comes with 4300 mAh battery with 30W fast charging and 30W fast wireless charging. It has 8 or 12 GB RAM, up to 2.84 GHz octa-core CPU and Adreno 650 GPU. It is powered by Qualcomm Snapdragon 865 (7nm+) chipset. The device comes with 128 or 256 GB internal storage and no MicroSD slot. There is an optical in-display fingerprint sensor in this phone.

title: Vivo X80 5G
description: Vivo X80 5G comes with 6.78 inches Full HD+ AMOLED screen. It has a middle punch-hole front camera design. The back camera is of triple 50+12+12 MP with PDAF, laster autofocus, OIS, 2x optical zoom, telephoto, ultrawide, Zeiss T* lens coating, Pixel Shift, dual-LED Flash etc. and 4K Ultra HD video recording. The front camera is of 32 MP. Vivo X80 5G comes with 4500 mAh battery with 80W fast charging. It has 8 or 12 GB RAM, up to 3.05 GHz octa-core CPU and Mali-G710 MC10 GPU. It is powered by a MediaTek Dimensity 9000 (4 nm) chipset. The device comes with 128, 256 or 512 GB internal storage and no MicroSD slot. There is an in-display (optical) fingerprint sensor in this phone.

title: Google Pixel 7
description:
Google Pixel 7 will be launched in October 2022. The Pixel 7 launched with a model number unknown. Firstly, Its dimensional measure is 155.6 x 73.2 x 8.7 mm and the weight is 195.5 grams. Secondly, the display of Pixel 7 is a 6.32-inch AMOLED panel with 1080 x 2400 pixels resolution. The display is protected from the unknown. Thirdly and most importantly, It is powered by the Google Tensor G2 (4 nm) and runs with Android 13. Moreover, it has up to an Octa-core (2×2.85 GHz Cortex-X1 & 2×2.35 GHz Cortex-A76 & 4×1.80 GHz Cortex-A55) CPU.

The Google Pixel 7 phone has a dual-camera setup on the back. This formation consists of a 50MP wide, 12MP ultrawide camera. It has a 10.8MP selfie camera inside the notch of the display. The video recording capability is 1080p@30fps. According to its RAM and ROM, It has two (8GB/128/256GB) variants. On the other hand, it can support up to microSDXC using a dedicated slot. Certainly, the Pixel 7 has a 4355mAh battery with 30W fast charging. It has a dual nano-SIM card slot. That is to say, Pixel 7 is 2G/3G/4G/5G supportable. The fingerprint sensor is under the display.
